# min dockerfile:

```dockerfile
FROM python:alpine
WORKDIR /app
COPY . .
CMD ["python", "main.py"]
```

# FROM python:alpine
- base dkrimg
# WORKDIR /app
- create dir in dkrimg in / dir
- cd in /app
# CPY . .
- (.)dot - if dkf in rootprj - ALL files prj
- be copyed to /app as (pwd) in imj
# CMD ["python", "main.py"]
- `$ python main.py` init command, analog `dkr exec`
